                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://medium.com/prysmeconomics/a-framework-for-blockchain-governance-design-the-prysm-group-wheel-703279c1b0dd?source=user_profile---------0----------------------------",
                      "meta": [
                        {
                          "id": "rel",
                          "value": "noopener follow"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "A Framework for Blockchain Governance Design: The Prysm Group Wheel"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Author: "
                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://medium.com/@cathybarreraphd?source=post_page-----703279c1b0dd--------------------------------",
                      "meta": [
                        {
                          "id": "rel",
                          "value": "noopener follow"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Cathy Barrera, PhD"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "heading",
                  "level": 2,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Summary & Commentary"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "The piece articulates the difference between operational rules and governance in blockchain platforms, along with offering a structured framework for designing effective governance for such systems."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Operational rules are the regulations that guide daily operations in a blockchain platform. They determine the size of block rewards, dictate how the next block in the chain will be determined, and ensure contracts, markets, and token economies behave effectively."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Governance, however, involves the decision-making processes regarding changes or updates to the operational rules. It addresses unexpected events and unanticipated changes, allowing the system to adapt over time to inevitable market variations."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "The key takeaway here is that while operational rules are the backbone of a platform, governance is its lifeblood, allowing it to adapt, grow, and evolve."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "The Prysm Group Wheel is introduced as a useful framework for designing effective blockchain governance. The seven elements it suggests to consider are:"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "style": "numbered",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "marks": [
                                "strong"
                              ],
                              "value": "Scope of Decisions"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "value": ": Understand what decisions need to be made with the governance process and plan accordingly."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "marks": [
                                "strong"
                              ],
                              "value": "Stakeholders / Participants"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "value": ": Define stakeholders and their various objectives to ensure that decisions align with their wishes."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "marks": [
                                "strong"
                              ],
                              "value": "Policy Research and Development"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "value": ": Prepare a specific proposal to implement a decision, especially for blockchain projects where decisions have to be translated into code."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "marks": [
                                "strong"
                              ],
                              "value": "Proposal Process"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "value": ": Establish a clear process by which proposals are made."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
